        <para>It is becoming more and more common for publications to be electronic only, but often, both print and electronic versions of the same publication are
            presented. For this reason, a URL field is presented in all cases. Just as Identifier, this field occurs with every publication option - please be
            sure to make use of it whenever possible, both for the publication itself and for its container, since this will considerably augment the value of
            your record to others.</para>
        <para>Use of this field makes it possible to catalogue both print and internet publications with the Basic Input Forms.</para>
